race.comment: TEMPT FATE (1) was resuming when finishing sixth at this track in a Grade 5 (20.38). Sure to be fitter. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from three attempts. Tough to beat if on-song. HOLLY MAGIC (8) has a strong record this trip with three wins and two placings from nine starts. Missed the frame latest (20.27) when seventh over 366m at this track in a Grade 5. Makes strong appeal on best. FINNIS BALE (4) is one of the chances after a minor prize at this track and distance last time.
